description: Updates a Timestream for InfluxDB cluster.

parameters.name: dbClusterId
parameters.description: Service-generated unique identifier of the DB cluster to update.

parameters.name: logDeliveryConfiguration
parameters.description: The log delivery configuration to apply to the DB cluster. Configuration for S3 bucket log delivery. The name of the S3 bucket to deliver logs to. Indicates whether log delivery to the S3 bucket is enabled.

nested_params.name: s3Configuration
nested_params.description: Configuration for S3 bucket log delivery.

nested_params.name: bucketName
nested_params.description: The name of the S3 bucket to deliver logs to.

nested_params.name: enabled
nested_params.description: Indicates whether log delivery to the S3 bucket is enabled.

nested_items.name: dbClusterStatus
nested_items.description: The status of the DB cluster.
